        <h1>Dr Ed Wallitt</h1>
        <p class="founder_sub_title">Founder</p>
        <p>Ed Walitt is the founder and director of Podmedics. He qualified from Imperial College School of Medicine in 2008 and worked for four years as a junior doctor in West London - achieving a place on the prestigious St Mary's GP Vocational Training Scheme. He now runs the medical IT consultancy side of Podmedics - Kaizen Ursus - providing high quality software consultancy and development services to NHS Trusts and healthcare startups in the UK.</p>

